text: I'm LIVID. It takes a month for an application to go through all the bureaucratic corporate bs before it lands on the hiring manager's desk, and by then, they're no longer hiring.

author: コナー (Konā)
text:
Bitter? Who, me? Still crushing and crushed? It's more likely than you think.
Send help, heart hurts.

author: コナー (Konā)
text: Trust in the Muertos. They have your back. The Mighty Dead will see you safely through.

author: コナー (Konā)
text: Daring to enter kink professionally. To live my lifestyle unapologetically. Scared. But I know that I am meant to bring my spiritual work to the community. I pray that the Ancestors who paved the way aid me on this new beginning.

author: コナー (Konā)
text: Something big is around the corner. I feel it in my bones.
